  schema:description "After completing this lesson, you'll be able to explain what a [budget](../terms/budget.md) is and why it matters, prepare a simple operating budget, compare actual results to budgeted amounts ([variance](../terms/variance.md) analysis), and describe the different types of budgets businesses use." ;
